 2022-13592022-12-15,  CH,  ,  , 
ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of JULIE RAMONA YING WON JAI of Toronto, Ontario, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Brian Paul McBay, whose term has expired.
